&lt;p&gt;This improves consistency and formatting accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;h2&gt;


  4. Chain-of-Thought Prompting
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Encourages step-by-step reasoning.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ideal for:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Logic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complex problem-solving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


  Example
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Find the integral:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;‚à´ x cos(x) dx&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reasoning:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify as product of algebraic and trigonometric functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Choose Integration by Parts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Let u = x and dv = cos(x)dx.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply formula uv ‚àí ‚à´vdu.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Final Answer:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;x sin(x) + cos(x) + C&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Chain-of-thought prompting improves transparency and logical clarity.&lt;/p&gt;




